#GetYourTVTogether @directv #Ad

node.text: 🥁🥁🥁…the first iteration of the Serena Williams Design Crew Launch is finally here!! The Serena Williams Design Crew is a collective made up of incredible Black and Brown emerging designers and creatives who created this collection, and will inspire future generations to design with impact. I can’t wait to see how SWDC will continue to evolve and make waves in the design industry for years to come.
